Architecture Diagram:
Source CSV → Ingestion → Raw → Preprocessing → Processed → Streamlit Dashboard

Detailed Flow:
1. source/tickets.csv (Original Dataset)
   ↓
2. etl/ingest_csv.py (Data Ingestion)
   ↓
3. data/raw/tickets_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.csv (Timestamped Raw Data)
   ↓
4. etl/preprocess.py (Data Cleaning & Transformation)
   ↓
5. data/processed/tickets_clean_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.parquet (Processed Data)
   ↓
6. dashboard/app.py (Streamlit Visualization Dashboard)

Configuration: etl/config.yaml
Logging: logs/pipeline.log
Execution: run_pipeline.sh